{"tid":1565052,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"藍絲越黎越進步","createTime":"2019-09-13T03:56:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T04:10:22.000Z","uid":321462,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"56efd7813d7fbc150766f234f2b9ab836423dcde","tid":1565052,"uid":321462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T03:56:54.000Z","msg":"【獨家消息】暴徒末路 「803基金」班底曝光！ 成員以退休警及建制議員為主<br />\n<br />\n懸紅緝拿六月以來「反修例」相關違法者的「803懸紅報料網」，上月底上線後，在兩岸四地社會以及外國都引起積極反應；由於懸紅金額可觀，不少網民都相信「重賞之下，必有勇夫」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《港人講地》收到消息，「803基金有限公司」的「創辦成員」是前特首和全國政協副主席梁振英，其他董事包括兩位退休警務人員，包括曾任香港警察隊員佐級協會主席、現為該會顧問的陳祖光，以及退休警司叢培勝，相信他們的專業知識、關係及經驗，對處理懸紅案件如虎添翼。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n除上述三人外，其他董事包括各建制議員，即行政會議成員兼新民黨主席葉劉淑儀、經民聯立法會議員梁美芬、民建聯立法會議員葛珮帆和自由黨黨魁兼立法會議員鍾國斌等。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「803基金」班底實力雄厚，並且有廣泛的代表性，加上豐厚的懸紅和充足的資金，相信不僅對破案有幫助，並且對作奸犯科者有極大阻嚇作用。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源：大公報、文匯報（資料圖片）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.speakout.hk/%E7%84%A6%E9%BB%9E%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/48595/-%E7%8D%A8%E5%AE%B6%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF-%E6%9A%B4%E5%BE%92%E6%9C%AB%E8%B7%AF--803%E5%9F%BA%E9%87%91-%E7%8F%AD%E5%BA%95%E6%9B%9D%E5%85%89--%E6%88%90%E5%93%A1%E4%BB%A5%E9%80%80%E4%BC%91%E8%AD%A6%E5%8F%8A%E5%BB%BA%E5%88%B6%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1%E7%82%BA%E4%B8%BB#selected\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.speakout.hk%2F%25E7%2584%25A6%25E9%25BB%259E%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F48595%2F-%25E7%258D%25A8%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E6%25B6%2588%25E6%2581%25AF-%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%25BE%2592%25E6%259C%25AB%25E8%25B7%25AF--803%25E5%259F%25BA%25E9%2587%2591-%25E7%258F%25AD%25E5%25BA%2595%25E6%259B%259D%25E5%2585%2589--%25E6%2588%2590%25E5%2593%25A1%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E9%2580%2580%25E4%25BC%2591%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%258F%258A%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E5%2588%25B6%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E5%2593%25A1%25E7%2582%25BA%25E4%25B8%25BB%23selected&d=mymTsZ9rb3gbearwAuc4QQEDdXZq%2B7ycbDpBQOFx8Mg%3D&h=58ba2a49\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.speakout.hk/%E7%84%A6%E9%BB%9E%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/48595/-%E7%8D%A8%E5%AE%B6%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF-%E6%9A%B4%E5%BE%92%E6%9C%AB%E8%B7%AF--803%E5%9F%BA%E9%87%91-%E7%8F%AD%E5%BA%95%E6%9B%9D%E5%85%89--%E6%88%90%E5%93%A1%E4%BB%A5%E9%80%80%E4%BC%91%E8%AD%A6%E5%8F%8A%E5%BB%BA%E5%88%B6%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1%E7%82%BA%E4%B8%BB#selected</a>"},{"pid":"8029f04df5b82fd9a266302e8d856437c7c47e2f","tid":1565052,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T03:57:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"e1207dc4501a36cd35946e1f604f9d5a380629c3","tid":1565052,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T04:05:44.000Z","msg":"完全封鎖「大Lin王」後將隱藏所有該會員的主題、回覆及被引用回覆。如日後需解除封鎖，請於「帳號」內的「封鎖會員」中設定。"},{"pid":"02dd345706af258a11571dc75992fa0b7a554098","tid":1565052,"uid":321462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T04:10:22.000Z","msg":"有無IT狗可以屌屌個803<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}